{"tid":1535542,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Suicidal black metal樂隊Silencer主音Nattramn","createTime":"2019-09-03T11:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T15:07:19.000Z","uid":40662,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9ffada6cbb7c8e03a8dd37707e8154167233f9e4","tid":1535542,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QzLTtiQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQzLTtiQ.jpg&h=04f13103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSuicidal black metal樂隊Silencer主音Nattramn，講起呢個人，關於佢嘅網上傳聞真係多不勝數，有人話佢好仇恨人類，極度厭世，仲自斷雙手再接上兩根豬腳，俾人拉去精神病院冇耐他就逃走出嚟，之後返到家鄉又用一把斧頭襲擊一個年僅6歲嘅細路女，仲叫到場嘅黑警殺咗佢。各式各樣嘅傳言眾說紛紜，真假難辨，令呢位連真實姓名同出生日期都未經證實嘅神秘男人添上一層撲朔迷離嘅色彩。<br />\n<br />\n上面係小弟所寫嘅完整千字文，內裡有介紹Nattramn歷年來嘅音樂同一啲逸事&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.com/2019/09/Nattramn.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimeischanging2013.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F09%2FNattramn.html%3Fm%3D1&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=a7706130\" target=\"_blank\">http://timeischanging2013.blogspot.com/2019/09/Nattramn.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"f87ca664b4acc5073e861050de817138e992cf84","tid":1535542,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:36:38.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"c1d61bfb3adbb703b3b6a9b48fe0623f9d3f3c19","tid":1535542,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f87ca664b4acc5073e861050de817138e992cf84","tid":1535542,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:36:38.000Z","msg":"lm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11:56:36.000Z","msg":"最近唔聽呢啲音樂會癲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701139ac3c71ecf735cd098780dad5ac8b05f5d5","tid":1535542,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T11: